DbfCodePageException, DbfDuplicateFieldException, DbfFieldNameException, DbfFieldPrecisionException, DbfFieldTypeException, DbfFieldValueException, DbfFieldWidthException
public class DbfException
extends RuntimeException

This is the superclass of all dbf related exceptions. These exceptions are tightly associated with the DbfFile and DbfField classes.

See Also:
